Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------OPCN1-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------EDCN1-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------PREV-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.04,0:00:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和純一趁著暑假參加了巴士旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.74,0:00:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於玩得太歡而遭到了報應
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.81,0:00:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在被人丟在了公路的服務區
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.37,0:00:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不應該吃那個鰻魚茶套餐的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.47,0:00:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你意思是怪我咯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.92,0:00:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一你不也吃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.01,0:00:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是這樣說…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.51,0:00:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 別把責任推到我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.91,0:00:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.84,0:00:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.51,0:00:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那時我們還無法想像
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.41,0:00:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們身上接下來將會發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.27,0:00:59.70,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}邂逅的一瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.64,0:01:06.12,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}如命中相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.90,0:01:14.02,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}想要確定這份心情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.21,0:01:18.67,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}今天依舊陪君左右
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.09,0:01:20.39,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}愛上你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.42,0:01:23.41,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Check my soul Check my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:27.41,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}心湖泛起陣陣漣漪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.89,0:01:32.91,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}此刻與你一同邁步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.02,0:01:36.00,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Check my soul Check my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.12,0:01:40.08,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}聆聽心聲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.38,0:01:41.51,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}前行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.00,0:01:45.52,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}去感受內心的律動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:50.79,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}宛如夢幻的時間流淌著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.81,0:01:58.69,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}渴望凝望你雙眸中的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:02.68,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Check my soul Check my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:06.70,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}聆聽心聲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.05,0:02:08.09,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}前行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.65,0:02:14.59,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}去感受內心的律動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.39,0:02:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還真是倒楣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.54,0:02:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒想到會被丟在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰對限定商品和本地特產太沒抵抗力了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.25,0:02:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要繼續說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.56,0:02:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也說過「能吃到實在太好了」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有是有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.36,0:02:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但完全沒想過薰會把時間弄錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然已經考慮到時間可能弄錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就應該嚴厲地警告我這樣不好才對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.33,0:02:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是看你當時很想吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.54,0:02:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別只責怪我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都沒責怪你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這口氣不就是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.49,0:02:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是羨煞旁人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:02:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.63,0:03:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂越是吵架關係越好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.63,0:03:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之按剛才說好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.32,0:03:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送你們到附近的車站
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.38,0:03:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有勞了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.01,0:03:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在很不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.95,0:03:19.22,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,650)\pos(320,260)\t(0,800,\fs14)}棚町 薰篇\N\N後篇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.95,0:03:19.22,title1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,650)\pos(319,295)\fs17\t(0,800,\fs16)}旅 伴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.95,0:03:19.22,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,650)\pos(319,295)\fs17\t(0,800,\fs16)}旅 伴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:19.22,title1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,650)\pos(320,260)\t(0,800,\fs14)}棚町 薰篇\N\N後篇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒記錯的話 車站旁有一家溫泉旅館
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚你們就住那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.35,0:03:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是所謂的山間溫泉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.12,0:03:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面很淳樸 感覺挺不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一 水溫怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.19,0:03:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.58,0:03:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.33,0:04:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然那麼喜歡 就這樣定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.04,0:04:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 還好你們不是單獨出遊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俗話說出門在外靠朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.01,0:04:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像旅途上有個伴兒能使人放心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.88,0:04:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互助互愛的人情味在人世間是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.86,0:04:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.81,0:04:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是幫了我們大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 別再吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他人真好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 所推薦的溫泉旅館是走這邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.68,0:05:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.18,0:05:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那進去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.27,0:05:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.08,0:05:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會是害怕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這點小事怎麼會害怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.83,0:05:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.91,0:05:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被嚇到了吧 剛才
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你平常連遊樂園的尖叫遊戲都不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.48,0:05:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說 薰你害怕了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有害怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.01,0:05:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才只是裝作被嚇到的樣子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:05:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.87,0:06:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二位願意的話可以先去沐浴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是天然溫泉來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.73,0:06:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天店內只有您二位客人 請慢慢享受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.49,0:06:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡給人的感覺有點陰森
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去洗手間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.34,0:06:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.42,0:06:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.73,0:06:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰 難道你害怕單獨一個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.94,0:06:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都寫在臉上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.02,0:06:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說不是了 我這是陪你去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.35,0:06:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.90,0:06:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是走這邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.21,0:06:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.83,0:07:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼死死地貼在我背後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 看起來有這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你多心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.92,0:07:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的是什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.08,0:07:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.29,0:07:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一 你去看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.09,0:07:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你留在這
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.64,0:07:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 我也要一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.51,0:07:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.23,0:07:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在準備飯菜 請先去沐浴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.98,0:08:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那待會再見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.49,0:08:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.28,0:08:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別一個人先回房間 記得在這裡等我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰這個膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說誰是膽小鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.37,0:08:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡環境真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.99,0:08:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰 發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那邊好像有些什…麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我出去 變態
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.31,0:08:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著 別真的走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.96,0:08:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是角落的話 也不是不能讓你進來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.75,0:09:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.89,0:09:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的胸罩還回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.95,0:09:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一你這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.67,0:09:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那隻臭猴子 那可是我很喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好豐盛的飯菜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:09:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先吃哪個好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.99,0:10:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好幸福哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.06,0:10:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一轉眼心情就這麼好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.99,0:10:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這太好吃了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.23,0:10:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.25,0:10:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好飽好飽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飽之後突然就想睡覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.17,0:10:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 薰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.93,0:10:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.15,0:10:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.31,0:10:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心裡有些困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.01,0:10:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎樣和純一交往下去才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.95,0:11:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我分不清什麼是朋友什麼是戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.54,0:11:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我希望能在這趟旅途中弄明白它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.65,0:11:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這麼想的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.16,0:11:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.49,0:11:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的錢包呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.75,0:11:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先墊付好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎再次光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣 找到錢包沒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.20,0:11:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.69,0:12:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 忘在公共電話亭那了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時我太心急了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.43,0:12:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在怎麼辦 結了帳之後我也沒剩多少錢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知會這樣 昨晚就應該直接去車站
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後等首發電車才對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.43,0:12:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時我還沒發現錢包沒了 能有什麼辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.99,0:12:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說 薰也有不對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.05,0:12:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.92,0:12:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在服務區買一大堆零食
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把錢都浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.86,0:12:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才不是浪費
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.76,0:12:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和限定商品的相逢是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.22,0:12:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又要說「過了這個村就沒有這個店」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.16,0:12:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經聽膩這個理由了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.46,0:12:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是從哪邊來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰 確定走那邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是我的直覺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.27,0:12:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直覺？走錯了怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:12:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那純一走另一邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.53,0:13:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.36,0:13:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不該走這邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.74,0:13:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.99,0:13:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 純一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.81,0:13:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.04,0:14:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種地方有個車站真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.46,0:14:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 薰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那隻臭猴子 那可是我很喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.68,0:14:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我沒在看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看是看到了 不對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要部分一點都沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一你這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.36,0:14:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼 以前好像也發生過這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.76,0:14:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前也發生過？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.07,0:14:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前也做過被女生掌摑的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.01,0:15:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只是錯覺而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 突然笑出來還真是失禮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.41,0:15:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你臉上那個掌印
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.32,0:15:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼這麼用力打出一個掌印來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.00,0:15:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜中了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.02,0:15:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰的直覺 你不是說這邊有車站嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.61,0:15:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像說了很多過分的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.89,0:15:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還一味地責怪純一你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.90,0:15:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 都是因為我丟了錢包
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.55,0:15:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 是我堅持要吃鰻魚茶套餐的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.95,0:15:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 就像純一說的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.04,0:15:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我買了太多限定口味的零食
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.38,0:15:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也說得過火了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.83,0:16:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.05,0:16:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.26,0:16:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.28,0:16:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅程才一半 快樂地享受後半吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.97,0:16:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓那些不愉快的事隨著雨水一起流走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真會說漂亮話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.62,0:16:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨停了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.66,0:16:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨終於停了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.35,0:16:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個 這個車站早就廢棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.04,0:16:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有巴士來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.54,0:16:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬幣就只剩這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.58,0:16:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 這裡是橘家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.33,0:16:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 美也嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:16:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.08,0:16:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也 其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:17:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說 今早旅行社那邊來電話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.07,0:17:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不太清楚是怎麼回事 但他們道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說 行李就由他們負責保管
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥你忘記拿行李了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.14,0:17:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但美也叫他們發到付郵件送回來 放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.85,0:17:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也考慮得很周到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.32,0:17:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 完全不用擔心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.90,0:17:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也 你先聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.82,0:17:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來老哥現在在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.94,0:17:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.82,0:17:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斷掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.85,0:17:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找派出所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.85,0:17:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 難得有機會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在這裡再玩一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.00,0:18:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一 快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.63,0:18:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.41,0:18:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.23,0:18:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過這次旅行我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管我嘴上說什麼 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.97,0:18:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要和純一在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.33,0:18:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會非常快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:18:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後也請你多多關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.97,0:19:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.38,0:19:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥們 棚町
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.79,0:19:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅原？為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.10,0:19:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個暑假 我有我的壽司修行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥們也有自己的男人修行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.44,0:19:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.43,0:19:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人修行進行得還順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.82,0:19:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常順利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.79,0:19:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羨慕死人了 哥們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.29,0:20:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.67,0:20:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得救了 薰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就是絕處逢生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣 我和純一的旅行總算告一段落
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.45,0:20:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是 這個高中最後的暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.06,0:20:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了我人生中最棒的暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.23,0:20:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.37,0:20:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.95,0:20:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘他還沒到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.91,0:20:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來找惠子你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.38,0:20:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.61,0:20:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事 我懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的 我有話想對惠子你說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.40,0:20:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是關於旅行的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.14,0:20:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假時已經在電話裡聽膩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:20:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就別再說了 感謝你的款待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.22,0:21:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想當面向你說聲謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.29,0:21:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 惠子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.48,0:21:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你推薦我去旅行那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.04,0:21:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.48,0:21:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它成了我的一份美好回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.88,0:21:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.95,0:21:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.99,0:21:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 純一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.69,0:21:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿著 幫你弄好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.31,0:21:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.74,0:21:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 很不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.55,0:21:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好 有人幫你做作業
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.05,0:21:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又耍花招 哥們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.26,0:21:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.45,0:21:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.68,0:21:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記畫燈塔了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.70,0:21:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.75,0:21:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.86,0:21:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰 你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.85,0:21:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還問幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.00,0:21:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是幫你把畫修好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.07,0:21:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.85,0:21:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.40,0:21:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.21,0:21:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意 別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.11,0:22:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是真正的我和你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.17,0:22:34.76,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}清晨傳來腳踏車的清脆鈴聲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.06,0:22:40.29,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}彷彿告訴著我時間逐漸流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.18,0:22:46.31,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}這份無法消散的情愫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.32,0:22:51.38,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}下定決心把它交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.81,0:23:03.39,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}點綴未來的預想於我身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.81,0:23:09.75,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}暗自祈禱當中有你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.25,0:23:14.55,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}於深秋落葉時深呼吸一口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.72,0:23:22.23,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}嘴裡吐出的卻是絲絲的嘆息
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.36,0:23:29.66,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}現在只希望你能聽我說一句
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.82,0:23:32.76,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.89,0:23:36.59,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}這便是我的告白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.82,0:23:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回預告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.66,0:23:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假快要結束了 時間過得真快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.77,0:23:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常言道 光陰似箭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.58,0:23:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.24,0:23:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來梅原你去進行壽司的修行了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.09,0:23:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我距離壽司職人又近了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.59,0:23:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人的階梯也和做壽司一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.70,0:23:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須一步一腳印地攀爬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.94,0:24:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.10,0:24:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘 原來你在呀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.43,0:24:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥們 你別愣在那兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.97,0:24:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.37,0:24:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.00,0:24:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜疑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.69,0:24:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 旁白的那個人呢
